-- Whitney Predicts `Very Weak' Year-End Wall Street Bonuses, 80,000 Layoffs
-- B y   J o h n   T u c k e r
-- 2010-09-30T11:16:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-30/whitney-predicts-very-weak-year-end-wall-street-bonuses-80-000-layoffs.html
Wall Street’s year-end bonuses will
be “very weak,” and as many as 80,000 layoffs may be required
by the U.S. financial industry, Meredith Whitney, chief
executive officer and founder of Meredith Whitney Advisory
Group, told Bloomberg Radio in an interview today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
JoAnne Norton at 
 jnorton@bloomberg.net  